x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23134024\/sun-machu-picchu-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23134024\/sun-machu-picchu-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23134024\/sun-machu-picchu.jpg 1536w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23134024\/sun-machu-picchu-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23134024\/sun-machu-picchu-648x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Please note: <\/strong>It is prohibited to take food, tripods, selfie sticks, and drones.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The first bus departs at 5:30 AM. However, make sure to start queueing at 4:30 AM as the line can get extremely long. Don&#x2019;t let the length of the line scare you; the shuttle buses are very convenient and fast.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also:<\/strong> Discover the surprising capital <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/lima-peru\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lima, Peru<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4>Hike from Aguas Calientes<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Your second option is to save a lot of money and hike about 60 minutes uphill to the entrance of Machu Picchu.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1.jpg\" alt=\"view machu picchu\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"307\" alt=\"view machu picchu\" class=\"wp-image-15312 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-600x409.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-450x307.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-800x545.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-1080x736.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-163x111.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-264x180.jpg 264w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-768x524.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133931\/inca-ruins-peru-1-1024x698.