oads\/2019\/07\/23133955\/ruins-machu-picchu-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133955\/ruins-machu-picchu-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133955\/ruins-machu-picchu-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133955\/ruins-machu-picchu.jpg 1484w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133955\/ruins-machu-picchu-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133955\/ruins-machu-picchu-626x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Huayna Picchu Mountain<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you bought a ticket that includes the hike to Huayna Picchu, please note that the gates to go up are only open between 7 and 8 AM or 10 to 11 AM. (Check the time on your ticket) &#x2013; To climb Huayna Picchu it is recommended to book your tickets 8 weeks in advance.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133920\/peru-machu-picchu.jpg\" alt=\"peru machu picchu\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"331\" alt=\"peru machu picchu\" class=\"wp-image-15321 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/23133920\/peru-machu-picchu.jpg 1920w